steps.name: I check that the "Welcome Screen" is displayed
I click on "GET STARTED" button
I check that the "Choose Data Preferences Screen" is displayed
I click on "ALLOW ALL TRACKING" button
I check that the "First SignIn Screen" is displayed
I click on "SKIP" button
I check that the "Notification Permission Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Location Permission Flow Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Location Permission Flow Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I skip linking my card
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "GAMES" button
I check that the application text: "GAMES" is equals to expected value: "GAMES"
I click on "GAMES" button
I check Games Top Area Text
I check that the application text: "Get ready to play & win with Ingo!" is equals to expected value: "Get ready to play & win with Ingo!"

parameters.name: Actual:
parameters.value: Get ready to play & win with Ingo!

parameters.name: Expected:
parameters.value: Get ready to play & win with Ingo!

steps.name: I check Games Middle Area Text

I check that the application text: "Simply log in to your account to continue. If you're not a member, sign up today and enjoy exclusive prizes!" is equals to expected value: "Simply log in to your account to continue. If you're not a member, sign up today and enjoy exclusive prizes!"

parameters.value: Simply log in to your account to continue. If you're not a member, sign up today and enjoy exclusive prizes!

steps.name: I check Games Play And Win Button Text
I check that the application text: "PLAY & WIN" is equals to expected value: "PLAY & WIN"
I click on Games Play And Win Button
I check that the "Sign In Screen" is displayed
I click on "SIGN IN WITH EMAIL" button
I enter the email "auto_freeliter@yopmail.com" in the input
I click on "LET'S GO" button
I check that the "Password Screen" is displayed
